# Shared JetBrains plugins, installed into every IDE by scripts/apply-jetbrains-plugins
# via the headless `installPlugins` launcher command. One canonical Marketplace
# plugin ID per line; JARs are fetched at apply time, never vendored. Only portable,
# non-language-locked plugins belong here (PHP/Terraform/etc. stay per-IDE).
de.netnexus.camelcaseplugin
org.sylfra.idea.plugins.linessorter
mobi.hsz.idea.gitignore
ru.adelf.idea.dotenv
